[size=+2]This is the new version of My Beautiful Enemies mod.For base on this mod i use armors and clothings from the AOM(The Art of Magica)mod.This mod adds hundreds of new unique sexy bosses with different beautiful clothes for each of them.All bosses have their own names,skills and abilities and each of them is strong for kill.[/size]

vanilla NPCs is not changed.[/size]
